{"tid":777341,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"考察全能的連登同志們一條智力IQ題","createTime":"2018-08-12T22:10:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-13T01:01:59.000Z","uid":66270,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"973865cc51147804fb710d227f2c6b150dd815ef","tid":777341,"uid":66270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T22:10:15.000Z","msg":"兒子：爸爸，呢個世界上真系有鬼嗎？<br />\n爸爸：無啊，仔，做咩啊？<br />\n兒子：我地屋企嘅保姆話世界上系有鬼噶。<br />\n爸爸：仔，快D執行李。<br />\n兒子：咩事啊?爸爸.<br />\n爸爸：我無請過保姆<br />\n兒子準備收拾行李回到房間見到保姆，大驚。<br />\n保母：咩事啊？<br />\n兒子：我爸爸話無請過保姆，你到底系咩？<br />\n保姆呆咗:你爸爸已經死咗4年了。<br />\n兒子呆咗，不知不覺倒地，撞到旁邊的桌子，花樽摔下粉碎<br />\n屋外經過的人：呢間屋已經5年無人住了，點解會有聲嘅？<br />\n<br />\n這里面其中有一個是鬼，是誰呢？<br />\n1爸爸 2保姆 3兒子 4路人"},{"pid":"c3624f0e628dec909aa6497277968e950b48a403","tid":777341,"uid":64318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T22:16:19.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"7d2f3d4c17cac1909efc8fb652a559655ce2f1e2","tid":777341,"uid":103212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T22:22:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dc2487bd7803c690df6393def8b6364006cb9140","tid":777341,"uid":64318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T22:23:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f40a27a7db77b38fd27a86ea14e464ecbea81d","tid":777341,"uid":159916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T22:31:26.000Z","msg":"個仔反應咁遲鈍，個老豆反應咁快，<span style=\"color: green;\">結論係</span>"},{"pid":"8ef8310cac9b8e737f21b4caf9ac5bac53fba633","tid":777341,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T22:34:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1073c0c97c74e9dcf931bc74df193f1352f9fc15","tid":777341,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T22:40:43.000Z","msg":"鬼同人都可以講大話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54764dc403a85f668441721950fdfc1b2979029b","tid":777341,"uid":40397,"like":1